content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Fremennik rings

The various Fremennik rings are each suitable for one of the combat classes and provide attack and defence bonuses that would be best used by a member of that combat class. They are dropped by the Dagannoth Kings in the Waterbirth Island Dungeon. The Fremennik rings are some of the very few rings in RuneScape to give stat bonuses, and are also some of the most expensive.

Players can also imbue the rings, increasing their stats, using either 650,000 Nightmare Zone reward points or 260 Soul Wars Zeal.
